      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAJOR SHIRAZ (6) charged out of the boxes with a slick early split and went straight to the front, giving a huge sight but headed late when a 4.5 lengths third (25.81) over 450m at this track. Likely to feature again. CHORUS LINE (1) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at Warragul over 400m behind Elite Intention (23.16) in a Grade 5 H. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Warrants plenty of respect. FIGURE OF SPEECH (3) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (25.88) last time in a Rank Limit - Grade 5 at this track. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. KRAKEN MISSILES (2) showed good early speed and won last start. Big chance on that form.",
